			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/CTY_Main_A\r\n- Use \"oe MT_Baptism\" and then \"oe MT_Court\" to start the baptism and teleport to the courtroom.\r\n- Walk to the room on the right - the abattoir - to find Valeria chained up there and saying this AD once you're nearby. She will play an AD every time after the cultists do two chants."
				},
